<!--Introduction-->

<div id="introduction">

<h3>

PNDISC CODE EDITOR allows you to test your websites not inside the editor but as a new window! This will allow you to see the website exactly like it would normally be and quickly. You just type the code bellow and click 'Run code'. You can also change the colors. Go to fullscreen to see more of the website background color. Sorry but on most phones there is not ennough space for the website background color.

</h3>

